snippet.title: Version 5.1 "The Rainbow Destined to Burn" Events Overview | Genshin Impact
snippet.description:
Genshin Impact Version 5.1 "The Rainbow Destined to Burn" will be released on October 9. Thank you for your support and companionship~
(*This is under development and is not indicative of the final product.)

Traveler, you can enable subtitles while watching!

Due to recording arrangements, this video will be shown with Japanese audio. We apologize for any inconvenience caused.
